# CODEOWNERS — Pricing domain and related CI protections
# This file assigns owners (teams or users) who must review changes touching
# the sensitive pricing domain, CI, and admin surfaces.
#
# IMPORTANT NOTES:
# - Pricing logic is financially sensitive and authoritative.
# - The pricing domain is the single source of truth; frontend must not implement
#   independent pricing calculations.
# - Pricing changes must remain deterministic, centrally governed, domain-driven,
#   and audit-safe. Any change to pricing logic requires review before merge.
#
# Replace the placeholder teams below with your real GitHub teams or usernames.
# These values are set to sensible repo-scoped team handles — replace if your
# organization uses different team names or user handles.

